---



## Tech Stack

- **Backend:** Spring Boot 4.0.5 (Java 25) — WebMVC, Data JPA, Security, Mail, Validation, AspectJ, Actuator

- **View:** Thymeleaf + `thymeleaf-extras-springsecurity6`

- **Frontend:** Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS · Tailwind CSS 3.4 (precompiled standalone CLI, **NO CDN**) · Chart.js · HTMX · Alpine.js

- **DB:** PostgreSQL 18+ (prod) / H2 file-mode (local profile)

- **Auth:** Spring Security + Email OTP (2FA) + Trusted Device + Single-Session Enforcement + optional OIDC SSO (prod)

- **API Docs:** springdoc-openapi (`local` profile only) — OpenAPI annotations in `controller/spec/*Spec.java` interfaces only

- **Local SMTP:** GreenMail embedded (port 3025) — OTP printed as `*** OTP CODE: NNNNNN ***` in server logs

- **Build:** Gradle Wrapper multi-module (`./gradlew`)



---



## Project Structure (Gradle multi-module)



```

oswl/                          # root — aggregates subprojects, tagged test tasks

├── oswl-scan-core/            # Manifest parser, BOM resolver, ScanPayload DTO

│   └── src/main/java/com/salkcoding/oswl/

│       ├── dto/scan/

│       └── service/ (+ manifest/, git/CloneRootPathGuard)

├── oswl-domain/               # Shared domain enums (entities remain in oswl-app for now)

│   └── src/main/java/com/salkcoding/oswl/client/

├── oswl-app/                  # Spring Boot application (bootJar)

│   ├── src/main/java/com/salkcoding/oswl/

│   │   ├── aop/               # Audit logging AOP

│   │   ├── auth/              # Auth module (config, controller, security, service, …)

│   │   ├── client/            # VCS clients (Bitbucket, VcsTokenValidator) — app-bound

│   │   ├── controller/      # Business controllers

│   │   │   └── spec/          # OpenAPI spec interfaces (annotations here only)

│   │   ├── domain/entity/   # JPA entities

│   │   ├── domain/enums/

│   │   └── dto/ exception/ repository/ scheduler/ service/ web/

│   ├── src/local/java/        # Local-only (TestDataController) — excluded from bootJar

│   └── src/main/resources/

│       ├── application.yaml / application-local.yaml / application-prod.yaml

│       ├── static/{css,js,img,icon,graphic,scripts}/

│       ├── templates/{auth,projects,security-center,…}/

│       └── db/

│           ├── migration/     # Flyway (prod): V7__api_key_machine.sql, …

│           └── *.sql          # Legacy manual scripts (pre-Flyway installs)

├── gradle/test-tags.gradle    # testFast, testParser, testIntegration, …

├── tailwind/                  # Tailwind input + config (build → oswl-app static/css)

├── docs/                      # English docs (synced to GitHub Wiki on main push)

├── docs/ko/                   # Korean docs (repo only; not Wiki-synced)

└── landing/                   # GitHub Pages landing site

```



Package names stay `com.salkcoding.oswl.*` across modules. `@SpringBootApplication` scans all jars on the classpath.



