## Domain Model (implemented)



```

Project → ProjectVersion / ScanResult → ScanComponent → DependencyPath

Library (shared) → Cve / LicensePolicyEntry

```



- **Project membership:** `project_members` + **Projects UI “Manage team”** (`members-panel.html`) + `ProjectMemberController`

- **Authorization layers:** (A) role-template permissions, (B) project membership, (C) system admin bypass

- **VCS push webhook:** `POST /api/import/webhook` + per-project webhook settings

- **Scan notifications:** Slack/Teams webhooks + email digest (`settings/tabs/notifications.html`)

- **SBOM export:** SPDX tag-value, SPDX JSON, CycloneDX via `LicenseController`

- **CI machine tokens:** `ApiKeyType.MACHINE` + `boundUser` — passwordless `POST /api/scan` when issuing with `{ "machineToken": true, "boundUserEmail": "…" }`

- **OIDC SSO:** `oswl.oauth2.enabled=true` + `OSWL_OAUTH2_*` env vars (prod); maps to **existing** users by email (no JIT provisioning). No OAuth login button in templates yet.

- **Flyway:** prod only (`ddl-auto: validate`, `db/migration/`); local uses `ddl-auto: update`

- **Not implemented:** Scheduled scans, SARIF, dependency-graph API, BillOfMaterials entity



