## API URL Map (actual endpoints only)



Full reference: `docs/API-Reference.md` · `docs/ko/API-Reference.md`



**Auth / Account**

- `GET/POST /login`, `GET/POST /login/otp-verify`, `POST /login/otp-resend`

- `GET/POST /setup`

- `POST /api/change-password`, `POST /api/my/change-password`, `/api/my/change-password/otp-*`



**Projects**

- `GET /projects`, `/projects/list`, `/projects/cards`, `POST /projects`

- Trash: `DELETE /projects/{id}`, `POST /{id}/restore`, `DELETE /{id}/permanent`, bulk trash endpoints

- `GET /projects/scan-status/stream` (SSE), `/projects/cli-integration`, `/projects/git-integration`

- `PATCH /api/projects/{id}/deployment-profile`

- `GET/POST/DELETE /api/projects/{id}/members` — team management (`PROJECT_MEMBER_MANAGE`)

- `GET/PUT /api/projects/{id}/webhook` — push webhook config (`PROJECT_UPDATE`)

- API keys: `POST /api/projects/{id}/keys` with `{ "machineToken": true, "boundUserEmail": "..." }` for CI tokens



**Quick Import** (session; `PROJECT_CREATE`)

- `GET /projects/quick-import`, `/api/quick-import/connections`, `/repos`, `/jobs`

- `POST /api/quick-import/start`, `GET /api/quick-import/job/{jobId}`, `/job/{jobId}/stream` (SSE)

- `POST /api/import/webhook` — VCS push → auto re-scan (per-project secret; CSRF exempt; set `OSWL_PUBLIC_BASE_URL`)



**GitHub API** (session)

- `POST /api/github/connect`, `POST /api/github/disconnect` (not DELETE)

- `GET /api/github/{status,accounts,repos,branches,branches/by-project,branch-updated-at}`

- `POST /api/github/repos/import`, `DELETE /api/github/accounts/{login}`



**VCS branches** (GitLab/Bitbucket): `GET /api/vcs/branches?projectId=`



**CLI Scan** (`ApiKeyAuthInterceptor` on `/api/scan/**` except `*/status`)

- `GET /api/scan/ping`, `/manifest-rules`

- `POST /api/scan/parse` (multipart zip), `POST /api/scan` (JSON + submitter email/password, or machine token)

- `GET /api/scan/{scanId}/status` — **session** (UI polling), not API key

- API keys issued via `POST /api/projects/{id}/keys` or `POST /api/admin/cli-keys`

- CSRF exempt: `POST /api/scan`, `POST /api/scan/parse`, `GET /api/scan/ping`, `POST /api/import/webhook`



**Security Center / Component Detail**

- `GET /projects/{id}/security-center`, `/print`, `/export?format=csv`

- `PATCH /projects/{id}/security-center/bulk-status`

- `GET /projects/{id}/components/{compId}` (HTMX fragment when `HX-Request: true`)

- `POST .../cves/{cveDbId}/ai-summarize`, `.../defer`, `.../create-pr`



**License / Exports**

- `GET /projects/{id}/license/export/notice`, `/export/spdx`, `/export/spdx-json`, `/export/cyclonedx`

- `GET/PUT /api/settings/license-policy`, `/api/settings/license-policy/{spdxId}`



**Analytics pages:** `/risk-trend`, `/version-diff`, `/scan-history`



**Settings / Admin**

- `GET /settings` (tabs: admin, security, ai, vcs, cli, cache, notifications)

- `/api/settings/{security,vcs,cache,ai,notifications}`, `/api/admin/{users,role-templates,audit-logs,cli-keys}`



**Observability:** `GET /actuator/health` only (SYSTEM_ADMIN session; prod)



**Public:** `GET /oss-notices`



**Local only:** `GET /data/test`, `/data/test-api-key` (`@Profile("local")`)



